cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR, cs.RO 

This paper deals with image synthesis and pose estimation, which are both topics related to computer vision (cs.CV). The use of disentangled representations and a disentangled variational autoencoder (dVAE) also suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper mentions the estimation of 3D hand poses, which could fall under graphics (cs.GR) or robotics (cs.RO) sub-categories.
